reviewText: Have been searching for a video that covers Moab, Utah and other parks in the West. Gives a great overview of the natural wonders, and it's almost like being there in person. Can't wait to go back there soon.
Exactly as described and priced. No complaint whatsoever. I would recommend the album and vendor. Everything went exactly as expected.
would recommend it to everyone, great pictures makes you want to go there to see them for yourself like we did
